# Connect resources to applications they serve
<https://w3id.org/noria/resource/server01.techcorp.com> noria:resourceForApplication <https://w3id.org/noria/application/DatabaseService> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/resource/vm-app-prod-01> noria:resourceForApplication <https://w3id.org/noria/application/CustomerPortal> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/resource/storage-nas-01> noria:resourceForApplication <https://w3id.org/noria/application/InternalCRM> . # CRM might use NAS for documents

# Connect agents to resources they manage (inverse of resourceManagedBy)
<https://w3id.org/noria/agent/DatabaseAdminTeam> noria:agentManagesResource <https://w3id.org/noria/resource/server01.techcorp.com> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/agent/NetworkAdminTeam> noria:agentManagesResource <https://w3id.org/noria/resource/router-core-01> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/agent/NetworkAdminTeam> noria:agentManagesResource <https://w3id.org/noria/resource/firewall-dmz-01> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/agent/AppSupportTeamA> noria:agentManagesResource <https://w3id.org/noria/resource/vm-app-prod-01> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/agent/TechCorpITOpsTeam> noria:agentManagesResource <https://w3id.org/noria/resource/storage-nas-01> .

# Connect applications to resources they use (via application modules)
<https://w3id.org/noria/application/CustomerPortal> seas:subSystemOf <https://w3id.org/noria/resource/vm-app-prod-01> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/application/DatabaseService> seas:subSystemOf <https://w3id.org/noria/resource/server01.techcorp.com> .

# Connect application modules to resources they use (more direct)
<https://w3id.org/noria/applicationmodule/CustomerPortal-Prod> seas:subSystemOf <https://w3id.org/noria/resource/vm-app-prod-01> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/applicationmodule/DatabaseService-Prod> seas:subSystemOf <https://w3id.org/noria/resource/server01.techcorp.com> .

# Connect services to application modules they comprise
<https://w3id.org/noria/service/PublicWebAccessService> seas:subSystemOf <https://w3id.org/noria/applicationmodule/CustomerPortal-Prod> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/service/InternalDataProcessingService> seas:subSystemOf <https://w3id.org/noria/applicationmodule/InternalCRM-Dev> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/service/InternalDataProcessingService> seas:subSystemOf <https://w3id.org/noria/applicationmodule/DatabaseService-Prod> .

# Connect trouble tickets to related parties (inverse of troubleTicketRelatedParty)
<https://w3id.org/noria/agent/AppSupportTeamA> noria:eventRelatedElement <https://w3id.org/noria/troubleticket/TT-20240315-001> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/agent/NetworkAdminTeam> noria:eventRelatedElement <https://w3id.org/noria/troubleticket/TT-20240316-002> .

# Connect change requests to related parties (inverse of changeRequestInitiatorParty, etc.)
<https://w3id.org/noria/agent/JohnDoe> dcterms:contributor <https://w3id.org/noria/changerequest/CR-20240320-001> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/agent/JaneSmith> dcterms:contributor <https://w3id.org/noria/changerequest/CR-20240322-002> .

# Connect event records to related elements (inverse of logOriginatingManagedObject)
<https://w3id.org/noria/resource/vm-app-prod-01> noria:eventRelatedElement <https://w3id.org/noria/eventrecord/ER-20240315-001> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/applicationmodule/CustomerPortal-Prod> noria:eventRelatedElement <https://w3id.org/noria/eventrecord/ER-20240315-002> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/resource/router-core-01> noria:eventRelatedElement <https://w3id.org/noria/eventrecord/ER-20240316-003> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/resource/router-core-01> noria:eventRelatedElement <https://w3id.org/noria/eventrecord/ER-20240316-004> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/resource/firewall-dmz-01> noria:eventRelatedElement <https://w3id.org/noria/eventrecord/ER-20240317-005> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/resource/firewall-dmz-01> noria:eventRelatedElement <https://w3id.org/noria/eventrecord/ER-20240317-006> .

# Connect event records to originating management systems (inverse of logOriginatingManagementSystem)
<https://w3id.org/noria/application/MonitoringSystem> noria:eventRelatedElement <https://w3id.org/noria/eventrecord/ER-20240315-001> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/application/MonitoringSystem> noria:eventRelatedElement <https://w3id.org/noria/eventrecord/ER-20240315-002> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/application/MonitoringSystem> noria:eventRelatedElement <https://w3id.org/noria/eventrecord/ER-20240316-003> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/application/MonitoringSystem> noria:eventRelatedElement <https://w3id.org/noria/eventrecord/ER-20240316-004> .

# Connect event records to originating agents (inverse of logOriginatingAgent)
<https://w3id.org/noria/agent/JohnDoe> noria:eventRelatedElement <https://w3id.org/noria/eventrecord/ER-20240317-005> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/agent/JohnDoe> noria:eventRelatedElement <https://w3id.org/noria/eventrecord/ER-20240317-006> .

# Connect trouble tickets to their notes
<https://w3id.org/noria/troubleticket/TT-20240315-001> dcterms:hasPart <https://w3id.org/noria/troubleticketnote/TTN-20240315-001-01> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/troubleticket/TT-20240315-001> dcterms:hasPart <https://w3id.org/noria/troubleticketnote/TTN-20240315-001-02> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/troubleticket/TT-20240316-002> dcterms:hasPart <https://w3id.org/noria/troubleticketnote/TTN-20240316-002-01> .

# Connect operation plans to change requests (as specifications or related procedures)
<https://w3id.org/noria/changerequest/CR-20240320-001> noria:changeRequestSpecification <kos/ChangeRequest/specification/FirewallFirmwareUpdate> .
# While noria:changeRequestSpecification is an ObjectProperty to a SKOS Concept, we can also imply a relation to the OperationPlan itself for richer context.
# This is not directly supported by the schema as noria:changeRequestSpecification ranges to a SKOS Concept, not noria:OperationPlan.
# However, we can use pep:usedProcedure for the ChangeRequest itself if we consider the CR as a ProcedureExecutionContainer.
<https://w3id.org/noria/changerequest/CR-20240320-001> pep:usedProcedure <https://w3id.org/noria/operationplan/FirewallFirmwareUpgradePlan> .

# Connect event records to proposed repair actions (if applicable)
<https://w3id.org/noria/eventrecord/ER-20240316-003> noria:alarmProposedRepairAction <https://w3id.org/noria/operationplan/ServerRestartProcedure> . # Example: if router interface flapping, a restart might be proposed.

# Connect event records to mitigation actions
<https://w3id.org/noria/eventrecord/ER-20240315-002> noria:alarmMitigatedBy <https://w3id.org/noria/troubleticket/TT-20240315-001> . # The TT itself acts as a container for mitigation actions.
<https://w3id.org/noria/eventrecord/ER-20240316-003> noria:alarmMitigatedBy <https://w3id.org/noria/troubleticket/TT-20240316-002> .

# Connect network interfaces to network links
<https://w3id.org/noria/networkinterface/server01-eth0> noria:networkInterfaceConnects <https://w3id.org/noria/networklink/link-dc1-server-core> .
