<https://w3id.org/noria/networkinterface/firewall-dmz-01-eth2> noria:networkInterfaceConnects <https://w3id.org/noria/networklink/link-dc1-router-firewall> .
<https://w3id.org/noria/networkinterface/firewall-dmz-01-eth1> noria:networkInterfaceConnects <https://w3id.org/noria/networklink/link-dmz-internet> .

