<https://w3id.org/noria/agent/TechCorpITOpsTeam> noria:agentManagesResource <https://w3id.org/noria/resource/router-core-01> . # Shared responsibility
<https://w3id.org/noria/agent/TechCorpITOpsTeam> noria:agentManagesResource <https://w3id.org/noria/resource/firewall-dmz-01> .

