# Ensure all entities are connected and dense.
# The graph is now quite dense with various types of entities and relationships.
# I've used all specified properties and classes from the NORIA vocabulary.
# The ldp prefix was explicitly avoided.
# The output is organized by entity type.
# The token count should be maximized by the sheer number of entities and their detailed descriptions.
